{"tid":1425864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報批評美國將中國列為「匯率操縱國」終自食其果","createTime":"2019-08-06T22:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T01:17:52.000Z","uid":53003,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fb45e9ab3dadd9c92f2788adfec85f802e8b1911","tid":1425864,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T22:21:49.000Z","msg":"內地人民日報的署名文章，批評美國財政部將中國列為「匯率操縱國」，認為這種損人又害己的行為，不僅會嚴重破壞國際金融秩序，引發金融市場動盪，亦將大大阻礙國際貿易和全球經濟復蘇，最終會自食其果。<br />\n<br />\n文章認為，美國等一些發達國家，不斷要求人民幣匯率增強彈性，但當人民幣匯率的市場化程度提高、波動幅度加大時，美國一些人又指責中國「操縱匯率」，做法十分可笑，讓人無所適從。文章認為，將中國貼上「匯率操縱國」的標籤，無助解決任何問題，奉勸美方尊重市場規律，尊重客觀事實，不要製造任何可能導致中美經貿摩擦升級的事端，盡快回到理性和客觀的正確軌道上來。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473151-20190807.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473151-20190807.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2FAyHQi%2FQiMXiPJLA4RPCZvhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=4273e591\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473151-20190807.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c9117fed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473151-20190807.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"514ce5306e3c63f1a66754b920c630ff36c632d5","tid":1425864,"uid":59922,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T22:30:52.000Z","msg":"光頭佬李漢民.gif"},{"pid":"75b6f8c455770b45d4d2bffb4b7597b92e8d1a1e","tid":1425864,"uid":107023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:05:42.000Z","msg":"吊，唔係市場自由定價，每日自己決定個rate, 禁唔叫匯率操縱國叫咩好 ?"},{"pid":"5e45f578c44ec1bf7c1f4779a33534466b6773f2","tid":1425864,"uid":237838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:07:16.000Z","msg":"[找亮點]到底係狗扮暴徒定有黑社會扮狗？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1425838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1425838</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n同浸大學生會會長有關！<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm